<p>The summer heat hasn&#039;t stopped your two favorite geeks — or you, with your questions — and this week&#039;s episode shows all of that and more. You&#039;ve had a ton of questions about audio devices and podcast management lately, so John and Dave dig into that first to re-open the doors on that conversation. Then it&#039;s on to tips and Cool Stuff Found, with a couple of return entries in the latter, including the very, very first Cool Stuff Found to ever have been mentioned! Press play, and enjoy watching (or listening) as you learn five new things.Note: Shownotes are in progress&#8230;</p>
